            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <div class="our-vision-text">
                    <p class="vt">Our Vision</p>
                    <h1>Creating an Inclusive Workforce</h1>
                    <p class="visiontext">Our vision is to build a more inclusive and diverse workforce where every person, regardless of their unique abilities, can find meaningful and gainful employment. We understand that talent knows no boundaries, and we are committed to dismantling the barriers that have traditionally limited opportunities for those with disabilities.</p>
